 Molteno - Police in Molteno are seeking the assistance of the public in locating a missing man, Lunga Jobela, aged 37 years. "Jobela is originally from Sterkstroom, but currently working at Molteno as security guard at the court premises," said police spokesperson, Capt Namhla Mdleleni. "He was last seen by his father on the 14 December and left without informing him where is he going. "He was last seen wearing  long sleeves maroon jersey, Blue Jean and black and white Tekkies." Capt Mdleleni said that anyone, who can assist with his whereabouts please contact Captain Bulelwa Ndiki at 0823018371 or 0860010111. Follow more RNEWS articles, subscribe to our YouTube channel and for breaking news LIKE us on Facebook. For news on the Western Cape click here. For great savings on life’s little pleasures visit Bargain Buys!  Know somebody who is getting married, Wedding and Function can assist.  Have kids, then you need to visit Kids Connection. Enjoy food and travel, then visit Home Food and Travel. Need assistance with an online presence, visit Agency One. 